 afr-ZA: http://grass.ru.ac.za/grass60/source/
 asi-JP: http://wgrass.media.osaka-cu.ac.jp/grassh/grass60/source/
 asi-TH: http://www.hpcc.nectec.or.th/grass/grass60/source/
